data.description:
Escape to tranquility in this stunning log cabin nestled on 11 +/- acres of natural beauty.  While the main floor beckons with two bedrooms, a family room boasting a fireplace and elegant hardwood floors you can entertain in style in the formal dining room and enjoy culinary delights in the granite-countered kitchen.  Ascend the spiral staircase to discover the master suite, complete with a garden tub and a convenient laundry area.  

Modern comforts blend seamlessly with nature.  Outside, a parking area and electric for a camper await complemented by a circular driveway.  Explore the established cleared paths, perfect for walking or riding, and immerse yourself in the abundance of wildlife that graces the property.  This is not just a home; its a retreat where each day offers a new opportunity to embrace the serenity of your surroundings.


Centrally located within 30 minutes of Vienna, Marietta and Athens.
